AUTHORIZATION
to create directory for storing private and public key use
mkdir app/authorization/cert

to generate_new rsa private key use following command:
openssl genrsa -in app/authorization/cert/jwt_private.pem -outform PEM -pubout -out app/authorization/cert/jwt_public.pem

to generate_new rsa public key use following command:
openssl rsa -in app/authorization/cert/jwt_private.pem -outform PEM -pubout -out app/authorization/cert/jwt_public.pem